				<td colspan="2"><span>I still say Shaman.  Shaman has the better buffs singularly of the 3.  Neither a druid nor a cleric can give you dex or agility.  The nice thing is that if you have access to all 3 then you can mix it up.  SLN with HoS chloroplast, staminia and agil buffs are absolutely awsome due to the total AC, hp, regen and agil/dex boost.
<br />

<br />
Without the dex and agility boost of shammy buffs you're denying yourself the ability to get your def and off up at a faster rate.
<br />

<br />
I still believe you should stay away from DS.  I also believe that Rushing to 10 via DS is silly.  If you can max offence and defence from the start you are better off in the long run.</span></td>
