				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Druid, shaman, or cleric for plvl<a name="26515"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Mar 9 04 5:28 PM</span></td>
