				<td colspan="2"><span>level 1-45: Druid. thorns, heals, buffs. lvl 2 AE dot will land on any mob just about and the exp will fly.
<br />

<br />
1-5:     Newbie area
<br />
6-25:   Paludal
<br />
26-40: CoM (not sure how it changed on the revamp)
<br />
41-45: Lguk.. very good exp modifier, careful of the factioners, maybe ask to group with them and ae slow. at lvl 43 you can get exp from a 65)
<br />

<br />
43+ Group with a 65cleric and have them slaughter undead OR... cleric pulls with reverse DS, bufs and heals you. Id recommend this till your skills catch up. Ideally at 43 grp him with a 65 bard and have the bard swarm =))). If you want to kill by pullingsingle mobs and having the twink fight them, use the cleric over the shaman. The clerics reverse DS (MoKings, not Karn), superior healing and buff make him the best for PL. Shamans can slow and haste you, but while working on skills, definately use the cleric, a slow will just mke the mob die slower tot he DS. 
<br />

<br />
Stay out of pop zones for solo pulling for the twink to kill,t he mobs hit too hard. And dont forget at 43+you can roup him with any of your characters and havehim get exp...but his defence will definately suffer.
<br />

<br />
AFK and sing songs atnight for your instrument/singing skills.
<br />
</span></td>
